This includes:
New Center attribute to flag Centers excluded for FTE and Salary data (GrpIns Excl Flag)
Build hierarchy based on unflagged items on Center attribute GrpIns Excl Flag (GrpIns Centers)
New Center attribute to set Centers’ segment for grouping (Segment)
Build hierarchy based on Segment values on Center attribute Segment (Segment Centers)
acceptance criteria:
A new attribute GrpIns Excl Flag exists on the Center DIM
